import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import axios from 'axios'
import VueAxios from 'vue-axios'

Vue.config.productionTip = false
app.provide('axios', app.config.globalProperties.axios)  // provide 'axios'
new Vue({
  render: h => h(App),
}).use(VueAxios, axios).$mount('#app')
